<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Bachelor Party | FIORE</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <!-- Google Font: Playfair Display for luxury look -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
   <!-- AOS Library CDN -->
   <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

<!-- AOS Library JS -->
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.js"></script>
<script>
  AOS.init({
    duration: 2500,  // Animation lasts for 2500 milliseconds
    delay: 300,      // Delay animation by 300 milliseconds before it starts
    once: true       // Ensures animations run only once (when scrolling down) 
  });
</script>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-bachelor">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Bachelor Party Bash</h1>
      <p>Celebrate the groom’s last fling before the ring with style, energy, and unforgettable memories.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bride-intro" data-aos="fade-up">
    <p>
        The Bachelor Party is the ultimate pre-wedding celebration—a bold and unforgettable experience curated for the groom and his inner circle. From thrilling adventures to refined moments of camaraderie, every element is crafted to honor his journey, his friendships, and the excitement of the days ahead. It's not just a party—it's a legendary send-off into married life, filled with style, stories, and memories that last a lifetime.

    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Bachelor Party Content -->
  <section class="bachelor-party-section">
    <div class="bachelor-card" data-aos="fade-up">
      <img src="/img/bp-decor.png" alt="Bachelor Party Decor">
      <div class="bachelor-info">
        <h2>Ultimate Decor</h2>
        <p>Transform the venue with stylish decor – from bold neon lights to chic lounge areas, creating the perfect vibe for the groom and guests.</p>
        <a href="/decorators" class="luxury-button">Explore Decor Ideas</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bachelor-card" data-aos="fade-up">
      <img src="/img/bp-dress.jpg" alt="Dress Code Ideas">
      <div class="bachelor-info">
        <h2>Dress Code Themes</h2>
        <p>From casual vibes to sleek tuxedos, choose a theme that suits the groom’s personality and keeps everyone looking sharp.</p>
        <a href="/dresses" class="luxury-button">Check Dress Code Themes</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bachelor-card" data-aos="fade-up">
      <img src="/img/bp-games.jpg" alt="Fun Party Games">
      <div class="bachelor-info">
        <h2>Fun Games & Challenges</h2>
        <p>Get everyone involved with games like beer pong, poker, or even a fun scavenger hunt to keep the energy high!</p><br>
        <a href="/Bachelor_Games" class="luxury-button">Explore Party Games</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bachelor-card" data-aos="fade-up">
      <img src="/img/bp-food.jpg" alt="Party Food & Drinks">
      <div class="bachelor-info">
        <h2>Gourmet Food & Drinks</h2>
        <p>Indulge in delicious food, from mouth-watering BBQ to gourmet finger foods. Don't forget the signature cocktails!</p><br>
        <a href="/catering" class="luxury-button">See Food Options</a>
        <a href="/Liquor" class="luxury-button">See Drink Options</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bachelor-card" data-aos="fade-up">
      <img src="/img/bp-photo.jpeg" alt="Photo Moments">
      <div class="bachelor-info">
        <h2>Capture the Memories</h2>
        <p>Hire a photographer or create a DIY photo booth for hilarious and unforgettable snapshots of the night.</p><br>
        <a href="/photographer_collection" class="luxury-button">View Photographers</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bachelor-card" data-aos="fade-up">
      <img src="/img/bp-gift.png" alt="Gifts & Keepsakes">
      <div class="bachelor-info">
        <h2>Unique Party Favors</h2>
        <p>Send guests home with personalized gifts like custom shot glasses, mini bottles, or a custom thank-you note from the groom.</p>
        <a href="/GiftShops" class="luxury-button">Explore Party Favors</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
